doc.after: In 2013 nearly 16 000 students studied at Maastricht University 47 of whom were foreign Students in Maastricht can affiliate with a number of student associations international associations or debating societies They present themselves during the annual INKOM the general introduction week for new Maastricht students Furthermore Maastricht offers several cultural and sports activities in and around the city
